01:03:25.470 --> 01:03:27.054
Hey, uh, perhaps another time.

01:03:27.263 --> 01:03:27.805
That's...

01:03:28.014 --> 01:03:29.807
that's wonderful.

01:03:30.016 --> 01:03:33.519
